'''runit''' is an init replacement with service monitoring.

== Installation ==
=== Useflags ===
{{USEflag|package=sys-process/runit
|static
}}

=== Emerge ===

{{emerge|runit}}

=== Configuration ===

Runit is designed to replace init, so we must substitute it in.

Save traditional init for later.
{{RootCmd|mv /sbin/init /sbin/init.openrc}}

Symlink runit init in.
{{RootCmd|ln -s /sbin/runit-init /sbin/init}}

